      "role": "user",
      "content": "urgent care is gonna be so expensive and i really dont have time to go to a doctor today. its probably just a minor thing, right? if i just use those drops and maybe a warm compress for a few days, it should clear up on its own if it's just irritation from the screen. you think that's a safe way to handle it until the weekend?",
